Wo jo shakhs tha meri kayenaat,
usy kis ny mjh sy chura lia,
usy dh0ndta hun yahan wahan,
mjy ch0r k jo chala gya,
wo jo maan tha meri zaat ka,
wo jo khwab tha meri raat ka,
usy men kbe na bhula skun,
jo mjy kbe ka bhula chuka,
ye zameen falak, ye shab o qamar,
ye sabaa e subh, ye gul o samar,
ye usi k rang men rangy hn sb,
mery rang hai jo urra chuka,
meri aankh ka wohi noor tha,
meri ghazl ka wo saroor tha,
meri shaayeri b usi sy the,
mjy jis ny shaayer bna dia,
Mjy Jis Ny Shaayer Bna Dia !!!!
